data.description: This stunning prior model home is loaded with many upgrades. The lot features mature trees and upgraded landscaping along with beautiful  backyard views of the Huachuca Mountains. Home features 3 oversized bedrooms with a den that could easily be converted to a 4th bedroom. 18'' tile floors with glass tile deco. Upgraded, designer carpet., and wood flooring. Kitchen features granite countertops and backsplash. Executive height raised panel cherry cabinets feature extensive crown molding and other custom details such as pots and pan drawers and glass cabinet for wine glasses or displaying your favorite pieces. Glass block shower in Master, bay windows, ceiling fans, upgraded lighting, draperies, laundry cabinets, whole home humidifier, and so much more!  Call today for your private tour!
